node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'Short Story... A woman came out of her house and saw three old men with long white beards sitting in her front yard. She said, "I don't think I know you, but you must be hungry. SWIPE LEFT Please come in and have something to eat."'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people and text that says 'Short Story... "Is your husband home?" they asked. "No, He's out" she said. "Then we cannot come in" they replied. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'Short Story... In the evening when her husband came home, she told him what had happened. "Go tell them I am home and invite them in!" @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person and text that says 'Short Story... The woman went out and invited them in. "We do not go into a house together," they replied. "Why is that?" she asked.'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and text that says 'Short Story... One of the old men explained: "His name is Wealth" he said, pointing to one of his friends, and said pointing to the other, "He is Success, and I am Love." Then he added, "Now go in and discuss with your husband, which one of us you want in your home."'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person and text that says 'Short Story... The woman went in and told her husband what was said. Her husband overjoyed. "How nice" he said. Then let us invite Wealth. Let him come in and fill our home with wealth.'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'Short Story... His wife disagreed. "My dear, why don't we invite Success?" Their daughter in law joined in with her own suggestion: "Would it not be better to invite Love? Our home would then be filled with Love!"'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people and text that says 'Short Story... Her in-laws agreed. The woman went out and asked the three old men, "Which of you is Love? Please come in and be our guest." Love got up and started walking towards the house. The other two also got up and followed him...'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people and text that says 'Short Story... Surprised, the lady asked Wealth and Success: "I only invited Love: why are you coming in?" The old men replied together: "If you have invited Wealth or Success, the other two of us would have stayed out, but since you invited Love, wherever he goes, we go with him, wherever there is Love. there is also Success and Wealth!" @AWARENESS_OF'.
Photo shared by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 19, 2021 tagging @thegiladhanina. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text that says 'EXCUSES TRUTH GILAD HANINA'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bill Gates' 11 Rules You will Never Learn In School @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Life is not fair. Get used to it! Stop expecting life to hand you the things you think you deserve'. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says '2. The World doesn't care about your self-esteem. Start making something of yourself today. Right now. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. You will not make a six-figure salary after school. You will have to work hard for what you get. @AWABENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. 'Flipping Burgers' is not beneath your dignity. Swallow your pride and take that job you think is beneath you as a stepping stone. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. If you mess up, it's not your parents' fault. Stop spreading the blame around and take responsibility for your failures. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Your parents know something you don't. Perhaps, before you were born, your parents weren't as boring as they are now. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '8. Your school may have done away with winners and losers, but life has not. The result of an exam does not justify the means. It doesn't bear the slightest resemblance to anything in real life. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9. Life is not divided into semesters. Once life starts, it just goes on and on. So spend your time doing something worthwhile. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '10. 10. What you see on TV is not real life. In real life, people actually have to leave the coffee shop and go to jobs @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Signs of maturity: 1. Small talks no longer excite you. 2. Sleep is better than a Friday night out. 3. You forgive more. 4. You become more open minded. 5. You respect differences. 6. You don't force love. 7. You accept heartaches. 8. You don't judge easily. 9. You sometimes prefer to be silent than to engage in a nonsense fight. 10. Your happiness doesn't depend on people but on your own inner self. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Most people aspire to get rich, but only a few do.

The main reason is most of us have the wrong attitude or are too comfortable in the safe zone.

But if you want to be wealthy and successful, you need to sacrifice your old self - let go of your limiting beliefs and look at the great things that could happen if you change these negative behaviors.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Ho Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 1. Negative mindset. Mindset is everything. Before you begin any task, big or small, you must prepare yourself by having a positive mindset. No matter how much effort you put in, if you're thinking that you're going to fail, then most likely you will. @awareness_ofsuccess'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 2. Blame. Failures don't hold themselves responsible for their losses. They always have their parents, their friends, and even the government to blame. Their minds are too busy finding fault with those that surround them but then fail to address and fix their behavior to improve themselves. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 3. Instant gratification It is the reason why many struggle financially. Most only think about how they can spend money to satisfy their immediate desires. But spending on non-essential things is burning the resources that could help you fund your own business. S @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 4. Being a know-it-all Be humble enough to accept that you don't know much and need others to steer you in the right direction. Find someone who can mentor you to accelerate your success on a skill you want to master. In time you'll realize it's a far more effective approach than trying to figure things out on your own. S @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 5. Fear of failure. Successful people know that failure is a natural part of achieving a goal. While most don't dare venture into unfamiliar territory, those who reach their goals accept the challenge and take failure as a contributing factor to their success. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 6. Poor spending habits. Wealth is not really about how much you make but more about how much you keep. Working hard to earn some cash is a waste of time if you throw away your money on things that are not necessary. @awareness_ofsuccess'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 7. Procrastination Putting off a task that will contribute to your success is essentially going to delay it. Do what you can do now. Rest if you have to. Listen to your body, but don't mistake rest for being lazy. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich 8. Excuses Don't waste your mental energy finding excuses, and talk yourself out to doing things to reach your goals. Instead, focus that mental energy figuring out on how to make your dreams happen. @awareness_ofsuccess'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Negative Behaviors to Avoid If You Want Το Be Rich Drop two below if you needed to hear this!! @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.
Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on July 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '"Train yourself to let go of everything you fear to lose." YODA @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.
